data.description: This is truly one of Caloosa's best! Mature oak trees adorn this beautiful park like setting! Five majestic acres! Located in a prime location, very quiet and serene! Cement block constructed, three bedroom two and one half bath home! Kitchen has just been totally remodeled with white shaker cabinets and waterfall quartz countertops plus all new appliances! Luxury vinyl installed throughout in 2023!  Picturesque views from every window!  Wood burning fireplace.  New water system installed in 2022.  900 square foot separate detached cement block garage/workshop partially air conditioned! Cement paved driveway, completely fenced with entry gate. Small pond adds to the park like setting! This setting offers so many options! Come see this beautiful five acres!!!
